### connect

connect

The connect command has been modified.

Just before connecting, the following will happen:

The _sp_cl_info_server cvar will be set to the ip:port (or hostname) of the server you are connecting to.

The functions in the _sp_cl_on_connect cvar will be executed.

Synopsis:

```txt
connect
SERVER
```
Parameters:

- SERVER:
